Title: Relates to vacating records for certain proceedings
Summary: Provides for vacating records for certain proceedings.
LawCode: Rpld & add §440.10 sub 1 ¶(k), amd §160.50, CP L (as proposed in S.6579-A & A.8420-A)
ActClause: AN ACT to amend the criminal procedure law, in relation to vacating records for certain proceedings; and to repeal certain provisions of such law relating thereto
